title: DAZ3D - Barrel Vacuum Cleane
description:
A barrel vacuum cleaner with flexible hose and moveable attachments. Comes in 5 colors Blue, Green, Grey, Red and Yellow. There are preloaded vacuums with just hose, or with nozzle or with full attachments. Also includes with textures for a some fun looking eyes as well as 3 separate cable props. Includes a pose to set up the vacuum for use with the Genesis 3 Female. The hose comes with several pose controls to aid posing. Optimized for Daz Studio 4.9+ and Iray.
